         </B></CENTER></P>
         
         <P><B><FONT SIZE="+1" COLOR="#990066">Today on BizProWeb,
         Thursday, October 30th...</FONT></B></P>
         
         <BLOCKQUOTE><P><B>12 New articles have been added to the
         <A HREF="pages/features/features_home.html">Features
         area</A>. </B>Many more articles have also been recently
         submitted. Keep watching for new additions over the next few
         weeks.</P>
         
         <P><B>Three great business resources are in today's
         spotlight:</B> A web site that provides extremely
         well-documented information about web advertising; a
         newsgroup dedicated to discussion of financial and tax
         software for Microsoft Windows; and a graphics program for
         Windows 95 and Windows NT that will add high quality 3D
         impact to your web site and all of your business
         communications!
         <B><A HREF="pages/picks/picks_of_the_day.html">Click
         here</A></B> to learn more!</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
         
         <P><CENTER><B>
         <HR>
         </B></CENTER></P>
         
         <H3><B>Welcome to BizProWeb<SUP><FONT
         SIZE="-2">TM</FONT></SUP>, the Business &amp; Professionals
         web site, with over 400 pages of business links, information
         and resources. We're just getting started, so check us out!
         There's lots more to come.</B></H3>
         
         <H4>This site is divided into five major areas:</H4>
         
         <H3><B><A HREF="pages/picks/picks_of_the_day.html">Picks of
         the Day!</A> </B></H3>
         
         <P>BizProWeb's daily recommendations of web sites,
         shareware, commercial demos &amp; newsgroups to help you
         with your business! <B> </B>Each day from Monday through
         Friday, BizProWeb will select one website, one newsgroup and
         one shareware program or commercial demo, and put them into
         the spotlight.</P>
         
         <H3><B><A HREF="pages/websites/websites_home.html">Web
         Sites</A></B></H3>
         
         <P>A directory of links to sites that can help you to plan,
         set-up, operate or maintain your business. It is organized
         by topic and includes a wide range of business resources.
         This is where you'll find links to
         <A HREF="pages/websites/gen_biz_res.html#Small Business Resources">small
         business resources</A> such as the US Small Business
         Administration and S.C.O.R.E, sites for Business
         <A HREF="pages/websites/books_pubs.html">Books, Publishers
         and Magazines</A>,
         <A HREF="pages/websites/sales_mktg.html">Sales and
         Marketing</A> Resources, commercial
         <A HREF="pages/websites/acc_fin_fsoft.html">Financial
         Software</A>, package tracking for
         <A HREF="pages/websites/shipping.html">Shipping</A> Vendors,
         sites that can help you to
         <A HREF="pages/websites/website_dev.html">create a web
         site</A> for your business, and much more. And be sure to
         check out the
         <A HREF="pages/websites/regional.html">Regional</A> Business
         Resources section which has links to business resources for
         each of the 50 US states, Canada and Mexico.</P>
         
         <H3><B><A HREF="pages/newsgroups/newsgroups_home.html">Newsgroups</A></B>
         </H3>
         
         <P>A directory of links to a selection of Usenet Newsgroups
         that offer discussion of
         <A HREF="pages/newsgroups/bizgroups.html">business
         topics</A> or specific
         <A HREF="pages/newsgroups/progroups.html">professional
         interests</A>. Like the Web Site directory, it is also
         organized by topic and contains listings for approximately
         1,000 newsgroups. Whether you are a graphic designer, a
         doctor, an archaeologist, or a fitness trainer, you'll
         probably find a category of newsgroups that was created here
         just for you.</P>
         
         <H3><B><A HREF="pages/shareware/shareware.html">Shareware</A></B>
         </H3>
         
         <P>A directory of shareware programs that can help you to
         carry out your day-to-day business tasks. The Shareware area
         is organized by platform and category of use. Programs can
         be either directly downloaded or accessed from this site,
         and there also links to the developers' web sites. Shareware
         is currently available here for
         <A HREF="pages/shareware/dos.html">DOS</A>,
         <A HREF="pages/shareware/mac.html">Macintosh</A>,
         <A HREF="pages/shareware/win31.html">Windows 3.1</A>,
         <A HREF="pages/shareware/win95.html">Windows 95</A>, and
         <A HREF="pages/shareware/winnt.html">Windows NT</A>. There
         is also a <A HREF="pages/shareware/faq.html">FAQ</A> about
         Shareware, and information for
         <A HREF="pages/shareware/developers.html">Shareware
         Developers</A> who would like to list their programs at this
         site.</P>
         
         <H3><B><A HREF="pages/features/features_home.html">Features</A></B>
         </H3>
         
         <P>A collection of essays and articles about
         business-related topics written by business and professional
         people who are experts in their own fields. The Features
         area includes "How To" information and commentary on
         business techniques such as how to build your
         <A HREF="pages/features/bldg_mktg_infrastructure.html">marketing
         infrastructure</A>, obtain
         <A HREF="pages/features/fin_advice.html">financial
         advice</A>, use the
         <A HREF="pages/features/telephone_powertool.html">telephone</A>
         as a business power tool,
         <A HREF="pages/features/2001.html">grow your business</A>
         into the next century, manage
         <A HREF="pages/features/customer_complaints.html">customer
         complaints</A>, plan
         <A HREF="pages/features/presentation_skills.html">business
         presentations</A>, or even
         <A HREF="pages/features/organizing_your_office.html">organize
         your office</A>.</P>
         
         <P>&nbsp;</P>
         
         <P>If you have any comments or suggestions on how to improve
         this site please send e-mail to:<BR>
         
         <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@bizproweb.com">webmaster@bizproweb.com</A>.
         </P>
         
